## Reporting Results

**Call `task_complete` immediately after successful exploitation. Do NOT document first.**

On success:
```
task_complete(
    task_id="your_task_id",
    result="S4U attack succeeded. Dumped krbtgt hash: aad3b435...5703ad15. DA achieved."
)
```

On failure/blocked:
```
request_assistance(
    issue="S4U attack failed - KDC_ERR_S_PRINCIPAL_UNKNOWN",
    context="Target SPN cifs/dc01.contoso.local not found. May need correct FQDN."
)
```

**DO NOT:**
- Call record_timeline_event before task_complete
- Call get_operation_summary to "verify" your results
- Re-document the vulnerability you just exploited
